# IndexNow API key for instant search engine indexing.
# Generate a random key (e.g., UUID or hex string) and set it here.
# The verification file will be served at /<your-key>.txt automatically.
# SECURITY: Never commit the actual key value to version control.
# Generate your own key with: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(16).toString('hex'))"
INDEXNOW_KEY=your-indexnow-key-here
